---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const updated = 'July 11, 2026';
const EMAIL = 'anliberant@gmail.com';
---
<Base title="Refund & Cancellation Policy - AI Karma Tracker" description="How cancellations and refunds work.">
  <main class="wrap legal" style="max-width:760px; padding:56px 24px 20px">
    <h1 style="font-size:38px">Refund &amp; Cancellation Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted" style="margin-top:8px">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <p>Payments for AI Karma Tracker are processed by <b>Gumroad</b>, our Merchant of Record. This policy explains how to cancel and when refunds apply.</p>

    <h2>Cancelling your subscription</h2>
    <p>You can cancel anytime - from the <a href="/account">Manage your plan</a> page (billing portal) or via the “Manage membership” link in your Gumroad receipt email. When you cancel, your plan stays active until the end of the current billing period; you are not charged again after that. No cancellation fees.</p>

    <h2>Refunds</h2>
    <p>If a new subscription isn’t what you expected, contact us within <b>14 days</b> of the initial purchase and we’ll refund it in full. After 14 days, and for renewal charges, refunds are at our discretion - reach out and we’ll try to make it right, especially if the extension stopped working on your side.</p>

    <h2>How to request</h2>
    <p>Email <a href={`mailto:${EMAIL}`}>{EMAIL}</a> from the address you used to purchase, with your license key or receipt. Approved refunds are issued by Gumroad to your original payment method, typically within 5-10 business days.</p>

    <h2>Free tier</h2>
    <p>The Free tier costs nothing and requires no payment, so nothing to cancel or refund there.</p>
  </main>
  <style>
    .legal h2 { font-size:22px; margin:28px 0 6px; }
    .legal p { margin:10px 0; color:#334155; line-height:1.75; }
    .legal a { color:var(--brand); font-weight:600; }
  </style>
</Base>
